{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2620590/extras/tiny_gif_1.gif?t=1736997061\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2620590/extras/tiny_gif_2.gif?t=1736997061\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Save the town festival in <strong>Marron's Day</strong>, a silly pocket-sized adventure where you're a bunny!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play as Marron, a young bunny, and help the cute animal friends in town so that they'll sign up for stalls at the town festival! Enjoy the cosy and retro pixel art graphics as you explore the town. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2620590/extras/tiny_gif_3.gif?t=1736997061\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2620590/extras/tiny_gif_4.gif?t=1736997061\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A top-down town to explore and adorable animal friends to help </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cosy minigames to go with a heartwarming story!  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cute pixel art and beepy chiptune music </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Authentic retro gameplay - it can practically* run on the handheld game console of your childhood! </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2620590/extras/tiny_gif_5.gif?t=1736997061\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2620590/extras/tiny_gif_6.gif?t=1736997061\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">*(It really will run!)</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Controls:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can use a controller, or for keyboard, use the following keys:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Arrow keys: Move</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">S key: Action / Use fishing rod)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">D key: Cancel Reel in fish)</p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Festival Fanatic","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2620590/74d2d0969c0bd1365365bfcc398e8d4f3ccd3e5e.jpg"},{"name":"Fishing Expert","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2620590/b802d90debe940f3304f3a2cca03366ac18ea28a.jpg"},{"name":"Rock Researcher","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2620590/f91cca0553759cccde4bb3f8783d7355cab119a2.jpg"},{"name":"Battle Eraser Champ","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2620590/07f10f0f1b0d659bf3aa2a479c1ff4d5e0ff73c2.jpg"},{"name":"Dandelion Destroyer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2620590/f43089cae98b2970236635528f1767e50a4cad22.jpg"},{"name":"Prologue Player","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2620590/3a944d638b7dbaf1c4e9656648711333cd39cf55.jpg"}],"total":6},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2620590/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736997061","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2620590/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1736997061","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2620590/4327ea051df4523ada22b5103e823debcea1f239/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736997061","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2620590/4327ea051df4523ada22b5103e823debcea1f239/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736997061","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18},{"des